attributes.Long form description: The student assembles a table, begins by inspecting the pieces in front of him, continues to grasp the legs of the furniture, then turns it to screw the base of the furniture, making sure to tighten the hex socket heads. He then grabs the circle to assemble and screw it to the base, and finishes putting the tray in place.

attributes.Transcription: We will now build the side table from IKEA.
So please go ahead and assemble it.
